</center>

===绘制函数动画===
{{Wikibooks|Maple/绘制函数动画|绘制函数动画图}}
;二维动画
<math>f:=2*k^2/cosh(k*(x-4*k^2*t))^2</math>

with(plots);

animate(subs(k = .5, f), x = -30 .. 30, t = -10 .. 10, numpoints = 200, frames = 50, color = red, thickness = 3);
{|
|-
|[[File:Bellsoliton2.gif|300px]]
